sec.p:
The cusp may be generated due to the repetition ofknots or the repetition of control points. The cases of cusps on NURBS curve for degrees of 2 and 3 are summarized as follows:


single knot: triply control points (p = 3); double control points (p = 2);

double knots: double control points (p = 3); single control point (p = 2);

triply knots: single control point (p = 3).
